description: This release adds support for VLAN-tagged network traffic over an Elastic Network Interface (ENI). This feature is in limited Preview for this release. Contact your account manager if you are interested in this feature.
Adds AWS Secrets Manager Access Token Authentication for Source Locations
Add support for httpChecksumRequired trait. SDK will insert Content-MD5 header value for operations with this trait. To disable the behavior, users can unset computeChecksums config
This release enables fast cloning in Aurora Serverless. You can now clone between Aurora Serverless clusters and Aurora Provisioned clusters.
